":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24578,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/04\/02\/best-deed-salvation-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34636,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Best deed for salvation is to remember Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 2, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe son of Adam does not act with a deed better to save him from the punishment of Allah than with the remembrance of Allah.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 22079 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33059,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/02\/dhikr-heaviest-mizan\/","url_meta":{"origin":34636,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Remembrance of Allah heaviest on the Scale","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Salma reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNothing is heavier on the Scale than to glorify Allah, to praise Allah, to declare there is no God but Allah, to declare Allah is the greatest, and for a Muslim parent whose righteous child passes away yet\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32771,"url":"